Job Description
Digital Advertisia is looking for a creative and dedicated Creative Web Designer who will be responsible for the designing of various minor and major website projects which are under the process of development. The candidate must be skilled and experienced in website template designing, design web themes, layouts for web sites and web/mobile based applications ensuring a great user experience. The designer must be familiar with new techniques for designing fluid, responsive and adaptive designs.
Job Specification
Must have excellent skills in Photoshop, IllustratorMust be able to design Website UI/UXMust have understanding of site structure, navigation, UI principles,wireframes, and user flowMust be able to design top notch Logos, Brochures, Flyers and StationeryMust be able to design web 2.0 websitesMust be able to design & layout of e-mail newsletters, landing pagesMust be able to manage multiple projects from conceptualization to executionCross-browser coding experience with understanding of code optimizationFamiliar with JavaScript, jQuery, and Server side scriptingAbility to take PSD designs and build in HTML/CSS to W3C standardsSome knowhow of SEOSelf-motivated, able to work independently, and perform multiple tasks under minimal supervisionSpecialist level Graphic / Web Design skills, must be a very creative / innovative individual who can work on multiple tasks with minimum guidance under tight deadlinesGood Sense of color schemesMust have impressive portfolio to showTools Required:Corel DrawAdobe PhotoshopAdobe DreamweaverAdobe Illustrator
